data.description: Storybook charm with exquisite craftsmanship. built by Judge Ivanhoe over 100 years ago, with high vaulted ceilings, stone fireplace for cozy nights, and a large 1500+- open attic space for whatever your heart desires. 3 full bathrooms, updated kitchen, 4 bedrooms all sitting atop the originally built stone wall. Dragon not included.  Must see this one.
